"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月11日消息，彭博大宗商品高级策略师Mike McGlone认为，通货紧缩可能会在明年取代通货膨胀。大宗商品见顶和美国国债长期债券收益率下降表明，2022年通货紧缩力量有可能重振，这将对[比特币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)和黄金产生积极影响。比特币将有望达到10万美元，而黄金交易价格将达到2000美元\",\"timestamp\":1639484452,\"title\":\"彭博分析师：通货紧缩将帮助比特币价格在2022年达到10万美元\"},\"digest\":\"Rf1Y6ASTEPNCQhxd40Pll1CrhzmOnvUfoQkasFNacHA\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x98c366AE25A726257c539B2aD7F512aFA67B0306\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"NGDt606BHY_wkpye2QfoIeHj0ryu1VLM3UYSsn5AUKU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IwxpZ2WCaHNpwP8eb_syOmIL6WY1LMxdMn_2FDu9aCo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ExsLeUxWKy3pQ1rqS0jhTcjPvigl3P3XohbDK9ifC3PdMJwt5UixbFLScZpeRE2Yl-_svqGiC25Kl2B0nknXjw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x52cb7cc8a9415f7653c6ffec7c9d4576afdbaaf4ab47faab723ebc6f0237c62244049f00f096053e2ba50796199734de16a034f4280a04dff92d60e8926b61151b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"NGDt606BHY_wkpye2QfoIeHj0ryu1VLM3UYSsn5AUKU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IwxpZ2WCaHNpwP8eb_syOmIL6WY1LMxdMn_2FDu9aCo\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Rf1Y6ASTEPNCQhxd40Pll1CrhzmOnvUfoQkasFNacHA\"}"